The '''''Resolute''''' was a picket destroyer employed by the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]]. The ''Resolute'' was part of the [[Blockade of Corellia]] by the Alliance's [[Third Fleet (Galactic Alliance)|Third]] and [[Fifth Fleet (Galactic Alliance)|Fifth Fleets]].

